SIMPLE: interdental
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interdental
<hw>In`ter*den"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Situated between teeth; <as>as, an <ex>interdental</ex> space, the
space between two teeth in a gear wheel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Phon.)</fld> <def>Formed between the upper and
lower teeth; <as>as, <ex>interdental</ex> consonants</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interdentil</ent>⟦br⟧
